WEBVTT

00:00:05.806 --> 00:00:08.141 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:00:50.058 --> 00:00:53.770 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:01:04.656 --> 00:01:05.782 line:80%
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

00:01:05.866 --> 00:01:07.784 line:80%
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

00:01:07.868 --> 00:01:09.452 line:20%
PROMISING THE END, NOT FOREVER…

00:01:09.536 --> 00:01:11.454 line:80%
EXCLUSIVE: THE ROYAL COUPLE'S
MARRIAGE CONTRACT LEAKED

00:01:11.538 --> 00:01:12.747 line:80%
[reporters clamoring]

00:01:12.831 --> 00:01:15.000 line:80%
[reporter 1] Is it true that
the marriage is contractual?

00:01:15.083 --> 00:01:18.128 line:80%
[reporter 2] Is it true you plan to
divorce in three years? Please respond!

00:01:18.211 --> 00:01:20.463 line:80%
ROYAL ACADEMY
80TH ANNIVERSARY CELEBRATION

00:01:20.547 --> 00:01:22.299 line:80%
[reporter 3] Did you intentionally
deceive the people?

00:01:22.382 --> 00:01:24.259 line:80%
[reporter 4]
This is a betrayal of the public!

00:01:25.594 --> 00:01:26.761 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:01:29.431 --> 00:01:31.600 line:80%
[reporter 5] What has Castle Group
promised the Crown?

00:01:47.532 --> 00:01:49.701 line:80%
[clamoring continues]

00:01:49.784 --> 00:01:52.579 line:80%
-[reporter 6] Is it true?
-[reporter 7] Are the allegations true?

00:01:54.122 --> 00:01:55.248 line:80%
[Huiju] What are you doing?

00:01:57.626 --> 00:01:58.627 line:80%
Keep your eyes on me.

00:01:59.669 --> 00:02:01.171 line:80%
[clamoring fades]

00:02:07.218 --> 00:02:08.803 line:80%
[clamoring resumes]

00:02:13.516 --> 00:02:14.768 line:80%
[clamoring fades]

00:02:29.824 --> 00:02:33.745 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:02:34.287 --> 00:02:35.830 line:20%
EPISODE 9

00:02:42.504 --> 00:02:43.880 line:20%
Let's get you out first.

00:02:44.381 --> 00:02:45.382 line:20%
[Hyeon] Your Royal Highness.

00:02:46.257 --> 00:02:49.469 line:20%
It's swarming with reporters
and students outside.

00:02:49.552 --> 00:02:51.179 line:20%
What should we do?

00:02:51.262 --> 00:02:53.556 line:20%
-And the Royal Guard?
-We had dispatched the bare minimum.

00:02:55.308 --> 00:02:56.309 line:20%
[sighs]

00:03:00.647 --> 00:03:01.690 line:80%
I'll leave first.

00:03:01.773 --> 00:03:03.400 line:80%
-You two can--
-Your Royal Highness!

00:03:03.483 --> 00:03:04.651 line:80%
I don't want to.

00:03:08.905 --> 00:03:09.948 line:80%
Let's leave together.

00:03:10.031 --> 00:03:12.242 line:80%
[♪ intriguing music playing]

00:03:26.631 --> 00:03:28.091 line:80%
[reporters murmuring]

00:03:31.219 --> 00:03:32.762 line:80%
[reporter 1] There they are!

00:03:32.846 --> 00:03:34.639 line:80%
[reporter 2] Any words
for the people watching?

00:03:35.140 --> 00:03:36.433 line:80%
[reporter 3] Is it all true?

00:03:39.519 --> 00:03:41.271 line:80%
[reporter 4] Are the allegations true?

00:03:41.354 --> 00:03:42.939 line:80%
[reporter 5] What comes after divorce?

00:03:43.023 --> 00:03:45.358 line:80%
-Are you confirming the allegations?
-Your Royal Highness!

00:03:45.442 --> 00:03:46.693 line:80%
-Are you okay?
-Yes.

00:03:47.694 --> 00:03:50.363 line:80%
-Your Royal Highness, what say you?
-Are the allegations true?

00:03:50.447 --> 00:03:53.199 line:80%
-Your Royal Highness!
-Please give us a response!

00:03:53.283 --> 00:03:54.617 line:80%
[reporter 6] Are the allegations true?

00:03:54.701 --> 00:03:56.786 line:80%
[reporter 7] Is it true that
this is a marriage of convenience?

00:03:56.870 --> 00:03:59.539 line:80%
[both gasping, panting]

00:04:00.290 --> 00:04:02.542 line:80%
-Oh, no…
-They're tinted windows, Hyejeong.

00:04:02.625 --> 00:04:04.669 line:80%
Really? Thank goodness.

00:04:04.753 --> 00:04:06.588 line:80%
[panting]

00:04:12.886 --> 00:04:14.054 line:80%
Right.

00:04:16.473 --> 00:04:17.474 line:80%
[Hyeon clears throat]

00:04:19.517 --> 00:04:21.269 line:80%
[grunts] Why isn't this working?

00:04:24.647 --> 00:04:26.274 line:80%
They should be okay, right?

00:04:26.357 --> 00:04:29.027 line:80%
I think so.
They have Prime Minister Min, so…

00:04:32.447 --> 00:04:35.867 line:80%
Right. I should update
the Royal Guard. [chuckles]

00:04:35.950 --> 00:04:39.662 line:80%
Right. I should also update
the Royal Secretariat.

00:04:39.746 --> 00:04:42.165 line:80%
[reporter 1] Is there any truth
to the allegations?

00:04:43.833 --> 00:04:45.752 line:80%
[reporter 2] Any response
to the allegations?

00:04:51.174 --> 00:04:52.258 line:80%
[Lady Choi] <i>We must hurry!</i>

00:04:58.181 --> 00:04:59.390 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:05:01.309 --> 00:05:03.436 line:80%
Where are the Grand Prince and Princess?

00:05:04.604 --> 00:05:06.272 line:80%
You see, they are…

00:05:11.778 --> 00:05:12.862 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:05:18.493 --> 00:05:20.578 line:80%
Reporters are camped out
in front of the palace.

00:05:21.287 --> 00:05:22.789 line:80%
This should be the safest option.

00:05:23.373 --> 00:05:24.374 line:80%
[aide] Sir.

00:05:25.834 --> 00:05:27.544 line:80%
The party is asking
about the crisis meeting.

00:05:27.627 --> 00:05:29.379 line:80%
Tell them they'll have to wait.

00:05:29.462 --> 00:05:32.465 line:80%
Make sure no one talks to the press
to avoid speculative coverage.

00:05:32.549 --> 00:05:33.883 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:05:33.967 --> 00:05:36.386 line:80%
Foreign Affairs is asking
about the overseas tour…

00:05:36.970 --> 00:05:38.805 line:80%
-[Jeongwoo] Submit it in writing.
-Yes, sir.

00:05:49.023 --> 00:05:51.818 line:80%
[newscaster] <i>Amid growing fallout</i>
<i>from the leaked marriage contract,</i>

00:05:51.901 --> 00:05:55.655 line:80%
<i>the controversy is escalating</i>
<i>beyond a mere private-life scandal,</i>

00:05:55.738 --> 00:05:58.950 line:80%
<i>even drawing scrutiny</i>
<i>over the monarchy's credibility.</i>

00:05:59.033 --> 00:06:01.911 line:20%
<i>The alleged preferential treatment</i>
<i>the Grand Princess received,</i>

00:06:01.995 --> 00:06:04.330 line:80%
<i>and the suspension</i>
<i>of the Junghwajeon fire investigation…</i>

00:06:04.414 --> 00:06:06.833 line:80%
[fading] <i>…have emerged</i>
<i>as the central points of this controversy.</i>

00:06:07.458 --> 00:06:08.585 line:80%
[I-AN, distorted] Huiju.

00:06:10.211 --> 00:06:12.005 line:80%
-Seong Huiju.
-[Huiju breathes heavily]

00:06:15.800 --> 00:06:17.719 line:80%
-[normal] Seong Huiju.
-[newscaster] <i>In response, the Crown</i>

00:06:17.802 --> 00:06:21.264 line:80%
<i>has stated it is verifying the facts,</i>
<i>maintaining a cautious stance.</i>

00:06:21.347 --> 00:06:24.225 line:80%
<i>However, critics argue</i>
<i>that the possibility of the exercise</i>

00:06:24.309 --> 00:06:26.394 line:80%
<i>of private influence cannot be ruled out.</i>

00:06:27.520 --> 00:06:29.856 line:80%
<i>Both the Crown and the Cabinet</i>
<i>are reportedly conducting…</i>

00:06:29.939 --> 00:06:31.274 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:06:31.357 --> 00:06:33.818 line:80%
[newscaster] <i>However, neither has yet</i>
<i>released an official statement.</i>

00:06:38.364 --> 00:06:39.365 line:80%
Yes.

00:06:56.758 --> 00:06:57.967 line:80%
[Jeongwoo sighs]

00:07:00.303 --> 00:07:02.096 line:80%
Let's start by confirming a few things.

00:07:02.180 --> 00:07:03.473 line:80%
First of all,

00:07:03.556 --> 00:07:06.059 line:80%
did you two draw up
the marriage contract yourselves?

00:07:13.066 --> 00:07:14.525 line:80%
[exhales sharply]

00:07:14.609 --> 00:07:18.238 line:80%
Besides me, does anyone else know
that this marriage is fake?

00:07:18.821 --> 00:07:20.448 line:80%
Aside from my personal aide,

00:07:21.115 --> 00:07:22.116 line:80%
there's no one else.

00:07:24.244 --> 00:07:25.578 line:80%
Just Ms. Do.

00:07:32.001 --> 00:07:34.045 line:80%
I haven't discussed it
with the Royal Secretariat yet,

00:07:34.128 --> 00:07:37.298 line:80%
but they will most likely
choose not to respond.

00:07:38.633 --> 00:07:39.842 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:07:39.926 --> 00:07:41.427 line:80%
As long as the contract is real,

00:07:41.511 --> 00:07:43.638 line:80%
any explanation or defense
will only stir up more noise.

00:07:43.721 --> 00:07:46.057 line:80%
So, are you asking us to stay silent?

00:07:48.476 --> 00:07:50.603 line:80%
Yes. Precisely, Your Royal Highness.

00:07:54.857 --> 00:07:57.610 line:80%
Waiting for things
to die down could backfire on us.

00:07:57.694 --> 00:07:59.737 line:80%
We must wait until even that dies down.

00:07:59.821 --> 00:08:01.197 line:80%
It was only…

00:08:06.828 --> 00:08:08.121 line:80%
a farce in the beginning.

00:08:08.830 --> 00:08:10.790 line:80%
[♪ soft music playing]

00:08:18.423 --> 00:08:19.966 line:80%
"It only started out as deception."

00:08:21.050 --> 00:08:22.135 line:80%
Is that what you'll say?

00:08:24.345 --> 00:08:26.973 line:80%
The contract stipulates
a divorce within three years.

00:08:27.056 --> 00:08:28.141 line:80%
Can you guarantee

00:08:29.392 --> 00:08:30.518 line:80%
there will be no divorce?

00:08:39.569 --> 00:08:40.820 line:80%
Can you?

00:08:49.370 --> 00:08:50.705 line:80%
[knocks on door]

00:08:50.788 --> 00:08:53.416 line:80%
-[door opens]
-[footsteps approach]

00:08:54.751 --> 00:08:55.752 line:80%
Sir.

00:08:57.045 --> 00:08:58.171 line:80%
You really should see this.

00:09:02.884 --> 00:09:04.010 line:80%
Excuse me for a moment.

00:09:09.390 --> 00:09:10.683 line:80%
[sighs]

00:09:12.935 --> 00:09:13.936 line:80%
[sighs]

00:09:14.020 --> 00:09:17.065 line:80%
I wondered why that brat
would just hand over the company.

00:09:17.148 --> 00:09:18.733 line:80%
Turns out she had a whole plan.

00:09:18.816 --> 00:09:20.735 line:80%
What about that kiss over the palace wall?

00:09:20.818 --> 00:09:21.861 line:80%
Was that fake too?

00:09:21.944 --> 00:09:23.196 line:80%
Of course, it was!

00:09:23.279 --> 00:09:26.699 line:80%
Then what about when she collapsed,
and he carried her out in his arms?

00:09:26.783 --> 00:09:27.950 line:80%
Was that all just an act?

00:09:28.034 --> 00:09:29.744 line:80%
Babe, who cares about that right now?

00:09:29.827 --> 00:09:31.704 line:80%
Our family is about to be ruined!

00:09:32.705 --> 00:09:34.874 line:80%
Well, I'm just worried about Huiju…

00:09:34.957 --> 00:09:36.709 line:80%
-[phone chiming]
-What is it now?

00:09:37.877 --> 00:09:39.170 line:80%
What's with all the messages?

00:09:39.253 --> 00:09:41.297 line:80%
ANOTHER SCANDAL WILL BREAK THIS WEEK…

00:09:41.381 --> 00:09:43.800 line:80%
[journalist 1] <i>I wondered why Prince I-AN</i>
<i>would marry a love child…</i>

00:09:43.883 --> 00:09:45.885 line:80%
[journalist 2] <i>He clearly married</i>
<i>for Castle Group.</i>

00:09:45.968 --> 00:09:47.595 line:80%
[journalist 3] <i>So all that talk</i>
<i>about Prince Suyang…</i>

00:09:47.678 --> 00:09:49.639 line:80%
[journalist 4] <i>Was her fainting</i>
<i>at the wedding just a stunt?</i>

00:09:49.722 --> 00:09:50.890 line:80%
Babe.

00:09:51.516 --> 00:09:53.142 line:80%
What the hell is going on?

00:09:55.353 --> 00:09:57.355 line:80%
<i>As public trust in the royal couple wavers</i>

00:09:57.438 --> 00:10:01.317 line:80%
<i>following the leak</i>
<i>of their marriage contract earlier today,</i>

00:10:01.401 --> 00:10:04.737 line:20%
<i>incendiary allegations have surfaced</i>
<i>that Grand Princess Seong received</i>

00:10:04.821 --> 00:10:07.824 line:20%
<i>preferential treatment</i>
<i>even prior to the royal wedding.</i>

00:10:07.907 --> 00:10:11.202 line:20%
<i>Grand Princess Seong had previously</i>
<i>been identified as the prime suspect</i>

00:10:11.285 --> 00:10:13.454 line:20%
<i>in the Junghwajeon Hall fire</i>
<i>that broke out</i>

00:10:13.538 --> 00:10:15.581 line:20%
<i>during His Majesty's</i>
<i>Royal Birthday Banquet.</i>

00:10:15.665 --> 00:10:19.293 line:80%
<i>Some critics argue that the Grand Prince</i>
<i>may have intervened in the investigation</i>

00:10:19.377 --> 00:10:21.087 line:20%
<i>for personal reasons.</i>

00:10:21.170 --> 00:10:23.631 line:20%
<i>Some are even voicing concerns</i>

00:10:23.714 --> 00:10:27.301 line:80%
<i>whether he is connected</i>
<i>to the Junghwajeon Hall fire incident.</i>

00:10:27.385 --> 00:10:31.055 line:80%
<i>The political sphere is adopting</i>
<i>a cautious stance,</i>

00:10:31.139 --> 00:10:32.432 line:80%
<i>while the palace and the Cabinet…</i>

00:10:41.107 --> 00:10:42.191 line:80%
[I-AN] Are you scared?

00:10:45.319 --> 00:10:47.613 line:80%
You have to have honor
for disgrace to mean anything.

00:10:49.866 --> 00:10:51.659 line:80%
I've never had any, so I'm fine.

00:10:57.540 --> 00:10:59.000 line:80%
[I-AN sighs]

00:11:00.209 --> 00:11:01.419 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:11:05.089 --> 00:11:06.716 line:80%
Honor is all you have.

00:11:14.265 --> 00:11:15.266 line:80%
Are you scared?

00:11:18.394 --> 00:11:20.480 line:80%
[♪ soft music playing]

00:11:29.071 --> 00:11:30.072 line:80%
Yes.

00:11:34.327 --> 00:11:35.495 line:80%
I am afraid…

00:11:38.956 --> 00:11:40.291 line:80%
that my honor will end up…

00:11:43.294 --> 00:11:44.337 line:80%
harming you.

00:11:46.964 --> 00:11:48.382 line:80%
[door opens]

00:11:50.801 --> 00:11:51.802 line:80%
I believe it's best

00:11:52.428 --> 00:11:54.347 line:80%
for you both to return to the palace now.

00:11:54.430 --> 00:11:55.973 line:80%
What about all the reporters there?

00:11:56.766 --> 00:11:58.059 line:80%
Are you sure it's okay?

00:11:58.142 --> 00:12:01.938 line:80%
[sighs] They're planning a protest
outside the palace tomorrow morning.

00:12:02.021 --> 00:12:03.147 line:80%
A protest?

00:12:03.231 --> 00:12:04.607 line:80%
What are you talking about?

00:12:06.526 --> 00:12:08.945 line:80%
There's a rumor that
you're vying for the throne.

00:12:09.987 --> 00:12:12.782 line:80%
The Junghwajeon fire is being interpreted
to fit that narrative.

00:12:12.865 --> 00:12:13.991 line:80%
That's absolute nonsense.

00:12:14.075 --> 00:12:16.744 line:80%
[sighs] Securing your safety comes first.

00:12:17.286 --> 00:12:18.329 line:80%
Return to the palace.

00:12:25.253 --> 00:12:29.048 line:80%
It appears the protest cannot be stopped.

00:12:30.800 --> 00:12:32.510 line:80%
Nothing could possibly stop it now.

00:12:33.052 --> 00:12:36.347 line:80%
To be loved is to be hated
in equal measure.

00:12:38.975 --> 00:12:42.103 line:80%
Nothing stokes gossip like the downfall
of the high and mighty.

00:12:44.480 --> 00:12:46.023 line:80%
Did you deliver the message to Father?

00:12:46.107 --> 00:12:48.025 line:80%
He sent word that he is on his way.

00:12:51.904 --> 00:12:53.906 line:80%
[♪ ominous music playing]

00:12:55.950 --> 00:12:57.577 line:80%
Prepare to enter the Council Hall.

00:13:11.007 --> 00:13:12.091 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:13:12.174 --> 00:13:14.093 line:80%
You should make your way
to the Council Hall.

00:13:14.176 --> 00:13:15.177 line:80%
Now?

00:13:15.261 --> 00:13:17.888 line:80%
Her Majesty has summoned
the Office of Royal Relatives.

00:13:28.524 --> 00:13:30.735 line:80%
[royal relatives chattering]

00:13:45.458 --> 00:13:47.460 line:80%
[herald] Announcing Grand Prince I-AN.

00:13:51.005 --> 00:13:53.007 line:80%
[royal relatives grunting]

00:13:57.470 --> 00:13:58.763 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:14:00.806 --> 00:14:03.059 line:80%
Have you summoned the royal relatives?

00:14:05.978 --> 00:14:09.190 line:80%
-Let's discuss it privately.
-I do not wish to hear your excuses.

00:14:09.273 --> 00:14:10.983 line:80%
-Queen Mother.
-How dare you!

00:14:12.526 --> 00:14:14.070 line:80%
To deceive the people

00:14:15.112 --> 00:14:16.864 line:80%
and bring disgrace upon the Crown.

00:14:18.949 --> 00:14:20.951 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:14:23.329 --> 00:14:25.247 line:80%
Do you truly believe you can be forgiven?

00:14:34.674 --> 00:14:36.967 line:80%
You, who sold off your royal status.

00:14:38.010 --> 00:14:39.929 line:80%
And you, who purchased it.

00:14:41.305 --> 00:14:43.432 line:80%
You would do well to prepare yourselves.

00:14:47.103 --> 00:14:49.021 line:80%
I found it rather peculiar from the start,

00:14:49.105 --> 00:14:51.857 line:80%
how she seemed to have no regard
for royal tradition or decorum.

00:14:51.941 --> 00:14:53.150 line:80%
You should stop there.

00:14:53.234 --> 00:14:54.944 line:80%
"It is simply
because of her low pedigree."

00:14:56.779 --> 00:14:58.406 line:80%
That was my oversight.

00:15:07.623 --> 00:15:11.460 line:80%
You thought you could protect yourself
with that measly contract?

00:15:11.544 --> 00:15:13.963 line:80%
I cannot tell if you are naïve or foolish.

00:15:15.464 --> 00:15:16.674 line:80%
[breathes shakily]

00:15:24.098 --> 00:15:25.683 line:80%
Senior Sixth Rank, Choi Hyeon.

00:15:26.434 --> 00:15:27.518 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:15:27.601 --> 00:15:29.103 line:80%
Junior Sixth Rank, Do Hyejeong.

00:15:29.186 --> 00:15:30.604 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:15:30.688 --> 00:15:33.482 line:80%
Your superiors are unworthy
of an audience in the Council Hall.

00:15:35.151 --> 00:15:36.152 line:80%
Escort them out.

00:15:47.788 --> 00:15:48.789 line:80%
[Huiju] Your Royal Highness.

00:15:53.419 --> 00:15:54.420 line:80%
Your Royal Highness!

00:16:01.927 --> 00:16:02.928 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:16:04.305 --> 00:16:05.723 line:80%
[sighs] Your Royal Highness.

00:16:06.307 --> 00:16:08.434 line:80%
[breathes shakily] I'm fine, so just…

00:16:08.517 --> 00:16:09.894 line:80%
You're far from fine!

00:16:14.398 --> 00:16:15.483 line:80%
[exclaims]

00:16:15.983 --> 00:16:17.860 line:80%
Who clenches their fist this hard
out of anger?

00:16:19.653 --> 00:16:21.238 line:80%
Just look at this hand.

00:16:22.406 --> 00:16:23.532 line:80%
Stay put.

00:16:24.033 --> 00:16:25.659 line:80%
I'll have Aide Choi get some…

00:16:26.952 --> 00:16:29.205 line:80%
[♪ soft music playing]

00:16:30.247 --> 00:16:31.624 line:80%
[I-AN sighs]

00:16:32.500 --> 00:16:33.501 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:16:35.628 --> 00:16:36.629 line:80%
It doesn't hurt.

00:16:41.425 --> 00:16:42.593 line:80%
[I-AN sighs]

00:17:05.157 --> 00:17:06.242 line:80%
[Hyejeong gasps]

00:17:06.325 --> 00:17:07.326 line:80%
This is insane.

00:17:07.409 --> 00:17:08.994 line:80%
It's hit the lower limit.

00:17:09.620 --> 00:17:12.498 line:80%
What if the chairman calls me
to his office? That won't end well.

00:17:12.581 --> 00:17:13.582 line:80%
Hello.

00:17:15.125 --> 00:17:16.210 line:80%
Seriously?

00:17:16.919 --> 00:17:17.962 line:80%
[Hyeon] Aide Do!

00:17:18.546 --> 00:17:19.547 line:80%
Yes?

00:17:20.297 --> 00:17:21.674 line:80%
We have a problem.

00:17:21.757 --> 00:17:23.008 line:80%
Why? What is it now?

00:17:23.092 --> 00:17:26.387 line:80%
There's an article claiming
the Grand Princess faked her collapse.

00:17:27.388 --> 00:17:28.514 line:80%
What?

00:17:28.597 --> 00:17:29.890 line:80%
What are you talking about?

00:17:31.183 --> 00:17:32.184 line:80%
THE REASON WHY SHE FAINTED…

00:17:32.268 --> 00:17:33.269 line:80%
WAS THE COLLAPSE STAGED?

00:17:33.352 --> 00:17:34.353 line:80%
Huh?

00:17:35.271 --> 00:17:36.272 line:80%
It sounds like…

00:17:36.856 --> 00:17:38.524 line:80%
This is about to blow up in our face.

00:17:38.607 --> 00:17:40.734 line:80%
WAS THE COLLAPSE STAGED?
PRESSURE MOUNTS ON ROYAL FAMILY

00:17:40.818 --> 00:17:44.238 line:80%
[protester] Remove Grand Prince I-AN
as regent!

00:17:44.321 --> 00:17:45.906 line:80%
[protesters chanting]
Remove him! Remove him!

00:17:45.990 --> 00:17:48.534 line:80%
[protester] Grand Prince I-AN
and Seong Huiju must apologize!

00:17:48.617 --> 00:17:50.452 line:80%
[protesters chanting]
Apologize! Apologize!

00:17:50.536 --> 00:17:54.123 line:80%
[protester] Remove Grand Prince I-AN
as regent!

00:17:54.206 --> 00:17:55.833 line:80%
[protesters chanting]
Remove him! Remove him!

00:17:55.916 --> 00:17:59.211 line:80%
[protester] Strip Seong Huiju
of her rank immediately!

00:17:59.295 --> 00:18:00.379 line:80%
[protesters chanting]
Immediately! Immediately!

00:18:00.462 --> 00:18:02.464 line:80%
[♪ soft music playing]

00:18:10.472 --> 00:18:11.891 line:80%
We cannot wait any longer.

00:18:13.392 --> 00:18:14.393 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:18:14.977 --> 00:18:16.520 line:80%
They're going so far as to suggest

00:18:17.771 --> 00:18:19.607 line:80%
that my wife fainted for show.

00:18:22.359 --> 00:18:24.153 line:80%
I shall set the record straight myself.

00:18:27.531 --> 00:18:30.659 line:80%
Our marriage may have started
with a contract,

00:18:31.952 --> 00:18:35.205 line:80%
but everything we've shown the people
is genuine.

00:18:35.289 --> 00:18:36.373 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:18:36.457 --> 00:18:37.958 line:80%
Even if the substance found in her system

00:18:39.501 --> 00:18:40.628 line:80%
was one prescribed to me,

00:18:41.962 --> 00:18:45.299 line:80%
there is nothing I seek to gain
at the cost of her life.

00:18:47.801 --> 00:18:50.304 line:80%
What about the claim
that you're vying for the crown?

00:18:52.514 --> 00:18:54.141 line:80%
Will you deny that as well?

00:18:56.435 --> 00:18:58.312 line:80%
-Prime Minister Min.
-Answer me, sir.

00:18:59.104 --> 00:19:00.356 line:80%
Will you deny it?

00:19:05.736 --> 00:19:07.029 line:80%
If I do not deny it,

00:19:10.240 --> 00:19:11.951 line:80%
how would you respond?

00:19:20.292 --> 00:19:23.128 line:80%
"We do not need a king
who lacks the people's support."

00:19:23.837 --> 00:19:25.130 line:80%
That's how I would respond.

00:19:30.511 --> 00:19:31.679 line:80%
Thus, Your Royal Highness…

00:19:34.390 --> 00:19:36.308 line:80%
For the sake of the Crown and the nation,

00:19:38.560 --> 00:19:39.561 line:80%
I humbly request…

00:19:41.814 --> 00:19:43.023 line:80%
that you end your regency.

00:19:57.037 --> 00:19:59.039 line:20%
5 DAYS BEFORE THE CONTRACT LEAK

00:19:59.123 --> 00:20:00.124 line:20%
Sir.

00:20:09.133 --> 00:20:12.219 line:80%
They discovered traces of digoxin
in a goblet used in the wedding rites.

00:20:12.302 --> 00:20:14.054 line:80%
PHOTO 1: GOBLET CONTAINING
TRACES OF DIGOXIN

00:20:14.138 --> 00:20:15.639 line:80%
-[knocks on door]
-[door opens]

00:20:16.306 --> 00:20:18.183 line:80%
Sir, Ms. Lee Areum has arrived.

00:20:25.899 --> 00:20:28.360 line:80%
[stammering] I heard you asked to see me.

00:20:33.240 --> 00:20:34.742 line:80%
PERSONAL DETAILS: LEE AREUM

00:20:34.825 --> 00:20:35.909 line:80%
IN CHARGE OF THE NUPTIAL WINE

00:20:35.993 --> 00:20:38.078 line:80%
PARK MALJA, HER MOTHER,
BECAME AN ALCOHOLIC…

00:20:38.162 --> 00:20:40.330 line:80%
IN NEED OF FUNDS
FOR BROTHER'S KIDNEY TRANSPLANT

00:20:47.629 --> 00:20:49.173 line:80%
[Areum on speakers]
<i>I was instructed to simply grind it up</i>

00:20:49.256 --> 00:20:52.384 line:80%
<i>and rub it on the Grand Prince's goblet.</i>

00:20:52.468 --> 00:20:55.012 line:80%
<i>I had no idea what it was.</i>

00:20:55.095 --> 00:20:56.722 line:80%
<i>I was told if I didn't do it,</i>

00:20:56.805 --> 00:20:58.807 line:80%
<i>my brother's surgery might be delayed…</i>

00:21:01.226 --> 00:21:02.895 line:80%
[sighs]

00:21:03.854 --> 00:21:05.022 line:80%
Do you think it's true?

00:21:06.106 --> 00:21:07.274 line:80%
We'll have to verify it.

00:21:10.778 --> 00:21:12.196 line:80%
[sighs]

00:21:15.783 --> 00:21:17.284 line:80%
But I still don't understand why.

00:21:21.622 --> 00:21:23.123 line:80%
Did they really need to kill him?

00:21:25.334 --> 00:21:26.585 line:80%
I get that he was bothersome…

00:21:34.551 --> 00:21:37.096 line:20%
4 DAYS BEFORE THE CONTRACT LEAK

00:21:37.721 --> 00:21:38.722 line:80%
Prime Minister Min.

00:21:39.807 --> 00:21:41.975 line:80%
What could you possibly
be suggesting right now?

00:21:48.398 --> 00:21:50.192 line:80%
Here's evidence
proving it was a poisoning.

00:21:54.238 --> 00:21:57.324 line:80%
A staff testified that the Grand Prince
was the intended target.

00:21:57.407 --> 00:22:00.244 line:80%
She confirmed the substance used
and her cryptocurrency records.

00:22:01.161 --> 00:22:02.329 line:80%
She also testified

00:22:03.789 --> 00:22:05.958 line:80%
that the compensation
came from Lord INPYEONG.

00:22:07.668 --> 00:22:08.710 line:80%
This is slander.

00:22:11.380 --> 00:22:14.049 line:80%
How dare you suspect my father
on a mere servant's word?

00:22:14.133 --> 00:22:16.385 line:80%
-You are also under suspicion.
-Prime Minister Min!

00:22:16.468 --> 00:22:18.095 line:80%
Can you prove you had no knowledge

00:22:19.596 --> 00:22:21.056 line:80%
of Lord INPYEONG's actions?

00:22:30.440 --> 00:22:31.650 line:80%
[servant] Your Majesty,

00:22:31.733 --> 00:22:33.527 line:80%
Grand Prince I-AN has arrived.

00:22:47.749 --> 00:22:49.293 line:80%
His Royal Highness remains unaware.

00:22:53.630 --> 00:22:54.798 line:80%
Allow me some time.

00:23:03.724 --> 00:23:04.808 line:80%
[servant] Your Majesty.

00:23:05.642 --> 00:23:06.894 line:80%
Prime Minister Min.

00:23:09.313 --> 00:23:10.314 line:80%
Until tonight.

00:23:12.649 --> 00:23:13.942 line:80%
That is all I can provide you.

00:23:19.114 --> 00:23:20.449 line:80%
I shall send word.

00:23:34.838 --> 00:23:36.632 line:80%
What brings you here, Prime Minister Min?

00:23:36.715 --> 00:23:39.051 line:80%
I came to request her cooperation
in the investigation.

00:23:39.134 --> 00:23:40.677 line:80%
The Inner Court will be summoned tomorrow.

00:24:08.163 --> 00:24:10.123 line:80%
I'm here to discuss
the Anhwadang Hall staff.

00:24:19.091 --> 00:24:20.092 line:80%
Your Majesty?

00:24:23.679 --> 00:24:24.680 line:80%
[grunts]

00:24:25.931 --> 00:24:28.809 line:80%
I heard you were looking
to replace the attendants.

00:24:30.435 --> 00:24:33.230 line:80%
Are you feeling unwell?

00:24:35.440 --> 00:24:37.359 line:80%
The Grand Princess collapsed
at the wedding.

00:24:38.402 --> 00:24:40.946 line:80%
Now, the Grand Prince seeks
to replace innocent attendants.

00:24:42.239 --> 00:24:43.865 line:80%
The palace is in disarray, is it not?

00:24:48.495 --> 00:24:49.496 line:80%
[sighs]

00:24:59.756 --> 00:25:00.757 line:80%
[Huiju] Jeongwoo!

00:25:03.260 --> 00:25:05.095 line:80%
Should you be outside already?

00:25:05.178 --> 00:25:06.346 line:80%
Did the doctor…

00:25:06.430 --> 00:25:08.682 line:80%
[groans] I don't need to hear that
from you too.

00:25:08.765 --> 00:25:10.851 line:80%
My ears are about to bleed as it is.

00:25:10.934 --> 00:25:14.604 line:80%
It appears she is weary from all the care
the Grand Prince has taken

00:25:14.688 --> 00:25:16.273 line:80%
to protect the Grand Princess.

00:25:16.356 --> 00:25:19.693 line:80%
Given how devoted they are to each other,
producing an heir should not be…

00:25:19.776 --> 00:25:21.528 line:80%
What… [laughs]

00:25:21.611 --> 00:25:24.031 line:80%
…in the world are you talking about?

00:25:24.114 --> 00:25:26.283 line:80%
In broad daylight, no less.

00:25:26.366 --> 00:25:27.451 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:25:29.828 --> 00:25:31.413 line:80%
Are you free for a short walk?

00:25:33.498 --> 00:25:34.583 line:80%
Hmm.

00:25:35.459 --> 00:25:36.960 line:80%
How's the investigation going?

00:25:37.586 --> 00:25:38.754 line:80%
Are you getting anywhere?

00:25:40.047 --> 00:25:43.508 line:80%
Can we trust Royal Seoul Hospital?

00:25:44.301 --> 00:25:45.927 line:80%
If you want, I can have Castle Hospital…

00:25:48.889 --> 00:25:49.890 line:80%
What?

00:25:52.184 --> 00:25:53.310 line:80%
It seems real.

00:25:53.935 --> 00:25:54.936 line:80%
What does?

00:25:55.812 --> 00:25:56.813 line:80%
Your devotion?

00:25:56.897 --> 00:25:59.649 line:80%
[sighs] Devotion? As if.

00:25:59.733 --> 00:26:02.861 line:80%
Can't I even show
this much concern for my spouse?

00:26:07.657 --> 00:26:09.034 line:80%
My goodness.

00:26:13.038 --> 00:26:15.415 line:80%
You know our marriage is only for show.

00:26:16.792 --> 00:26:18.710 line:80%
How are we supposed to fool the nation

00:26:18.794 --> 00:26:20.462 line:80%
if we can't even fool the staff?

00:26:22.506 --> 00:26:23.507 line:80%
So?

00:26:24.674 --> 00:26:25.967 line:80%
You're trying to fool me too?

00:26:26.593 --> 00:26:27.636 line:80%
What?

00:26:30.597 --> 00:26:31.640 line:80%
[Mr. Jung] Sir.

00:26:37.312 --> 00:26:39.773 line:80%
His Majesty is due to give
his witness statement shortly.

00:26:43.568 --> 00:26:44.611 line:80%
I should go.

00:26:46.655 --> 00:26:48.073 line:80%
But I'm not done talking yet…

00:26:49.116 --> 00:26:50.784 line:80%
I'll call you later… [stammers]

00:27:02.504 --> 00:27:04.506 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>Evidence that proves</i>
<i>it was a poisoning.</i>

00:27:05.298 --> 00:27:08.385 line:80%
<i>A staff testified that the Grand Prince</i>
<i>was the intended target.</i>

00:27:08.468 --> 00:27:11.430 line:80%
<i>She confirmed the drug used</i>
<i>and her cryptocurrency records.</i>

00:27:14.015 --> 00:27:16.268 line:80%
<i>She testified the compensation</i>
<i>came from Lord INPYEONG.</i>

00:27:21.106 --> 00:27:22.107 line:80%
[door opens]

00:27:25.277 --> 00:27:26.278 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:27:26.903 --> 00:27:28.488 line:80%
What brings you here unannounced?

00:27:30.198 --> 00:27:31.324 line:80%
Explain yourself.

00:27:32.117 --> 00:27:33.368 line:80%
-Your Majesty.
-I said!

00:27:36.371 --> 00:27:37.622 line:80%
Explain yourself.

00:27:56.850 --> 00:27:58.143 line:80%
Tell me it was not you.

00:27:58.685 --> 00:27:59.895 line:80%
PERSONAL DETAILS: LEE AREUM

00:27:59.978 --> 00:28:01.688 line:80%
WITNESS STATEMENT

00:28:04.441 --> 00:28:05.984 line:80%
Where did you get this?

00:28:11.573 --> 00:28:14.075 line:80%
I asked where you got this.

00:28:15.994 --> 00:28:18.288 line:80%
Were you truly attempting to murder
the Grand Prince?

00:28:18.371 --> 00:28:20.373 line:80%
[♪ dramatic music playing]

00:28:21.958 --> 00:28:23.293 line:80%
Have you lost your mind?

00:28:23.960 --> 00:28:27.088 line:80%
If this gets out,
you, me, and His Majesty will be--

00:28:27.172 --> 00:28:28.173 line:80%
That is…

00:28:30.884 --> 00:28:34.054 line:80%
exactly why the Grand Prince
must be eliminated.

00:28:38.808 --> 00:28:42.479 line:80%
Why do you think the Grand Prince,
who feigned ignorance,

00:28:42.562 --> 00:28:44.940 line:80%
has chosen to speak up now?

00:28:45.649 --> 00:28:48.527 line:80%
Not only did you burn
the late King's final royal edict.

00:28:48.610 --> 00:28:50.111 line:80%
But imagine

00:28:50.862 --> 00:28:53.615 line:80%
what would happen if he discovers
the same fire killed the late King.

00:28:53.698 --> 00:28:55.617 line:80%
I had nothing to do
with the late King's death!

00:28:55.700 --> 00:28:57.285 line:80%
Who would ever believe

00:28:57.827 --> 00:29:00.163 line:80%
such a feeble excuse?

00:29:02.791 --> 00:29:04.543 line:80%
[breathes shakily] Father…

00:29:04.626 --> 00:29:06.586 line:80%
"I only intended to burn the royal edict.

00:29:06.670 --> 00:29:08.255 line:80%
I never intended for that fire

00:29:08.964 --> 00:29:11.800 line:80%
to burn down the palace hall
and take the King's life."

00:29:13.468 --> 00:29:14.928 line:80%
Is that what you will say?

00:29:22.435 --> 00:29:24.688 line:80%
Is that what you have thought of me
all this time?

00:29:35.156 --> 00:29:39.369 line:80%
What Your Majesty has done
is not my concern.

00:29:40.704 --> 00:29:43.206 line:80%
You must do whatever it takes
to keep His Majesty safe.

00:29:43.290 --> 00:29:45.458 line:80%
That is the only way

00:29:45.542 --> 00:29:47.711 line:80%
to ensure your own safety,

00:29:47.794 --> 00:29:49.963 line:80%
mine, and our family name.

00:30:05.812 --> 00:30:07.272 line:80%
Now, tell me.

00:30:09.441 --> 00:30:10.609 line:80%
Where did you

00:30:12.193 --> 00:30:14.237 line:80%
get this from?

00:30:40.513 --> 00:30:41.848 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:30:46.603 --> 00:30:47.604 line:80%
Grand Princess.

00:30:54.110 --> 00:30:55.820 line:80%
You would do well to tread carefully.

00:31:11.628 --> 00:31:12.629 line:80%
[intercom beeps]

00:31:13.672 --> 00:31:14.673 line:80%
[assistant] <i>Sir.</i>

00:31:14.756 --> 00:31:16.383 line:80%
<i>The Queen Mother is calling. It's urgent.</i>

00:31:16.883 --> 00:31:19.761 line:80%
-<i>I'll connect you now.</i>
-[phone buzzing, ringing]

00:31:23.223 --> 00:31:24.849 line:80%
HUIJU

00:31:32.482 --> 00:31:34.776 line:80%
[ringing continues]

00:31:40.824 --> 00:31:46.746 line:80%
3 DAYS BEFORE THE CONTRACT LEAK

00:32:26.870 --> 00:32:28.204 line:80%
How does it feel

00:32:28.705 --> 00:32:31.958 line:80%
to have the man hailed
as the greatest prime minister in history

00:32:32.917 --> 00:32:34.169 line:80%
as a father?

00:32:34.252 --> 00:32:35.462 line:80%
PRIME MINISTER MIN SEUNGJAE

00:32:38.173 --> 00:32:39.174 line:80%
I'm not sure.

00:32:40.341 --> 00:32:43.386 line:80%
How does it feel
to have a father who will be known

00:32:43.470 --> 00:32:44.679 line:80%
as the most dangerous lord

00:32:45.805 --> 00:32:47.182 line:80%
in history?

00:32:49.559 --> 00:32:51.519 line:80%
That will not be his legacy.

00:32:53.396 --> 00:32:54.481 line:80%
Are you denying it?

00:32:56.316 --> 00:32:58.026 line:80%
I wish to make a request.

00:32:59.486 --> 00:33:02.906 line:80%
I thought about what would lead you
to bring me that evidence.

00:33:04.991 --> 00:33:07.243 line:80%
If I were a suspect in your eyes…

00:33:10.163 --> 00:33:12.665 line:80%
why did you come to me
and not the Grand Prince?

00:33:16.044 --> 00:33:17.921 line:80%
Do you wish to have the Grand Princess?

00:33:25.261 --> 00:33:26.304 line:80%
[sighs]

00:33:43.488 --> 00:33:44.948 line:80%
MARRIAGE CONTRACT

00:33:45.031 --> 00:33:46.324 line:80%
Should that come to light,

00:33:46.407 --> 00:33:48.618 line:80%
the court will be in turmoil
and the nation in chaos.

00:33:50.954 --> 00:33:53.540 line:80%
All the benefits outlined in the contract
favor the Grand Princess.

00:33:53.623 --> 00:33:56.417 line:80%
Thus, the tide of condemnation
will break upon her.

00:33:59.796 --> 00:34:02.131 line:80%
Do you think I would just let that happen?

00:34:02.757 --> 00:34:04.843 line:80%
It is clear you are intent
on taking her for yourself.

00:34:06.845 --> 00:34:08.972 line:80%
And you do not want her to suffer, either?

00:34:12.225 --> 00:34:13.560 line:80%
Then,

00:34:14.978 --> 00:34:18.147 line:80%
I shall redirect that tide to Prince I-AN.

00:34:19.858 --> 00:34:22.861 line:80%
The more the Grand Prince
is driven to the brink,

00:34:23.862 --> 00:34:26.739 line:80%
the more her resolve
is bound to crumble, is it not?

00:34:29.784 --> 00:34:30.910 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:34:31.411 --> 00:34:32.537 line:80%
What is the matter?

00:34:33.246 --> 00:34:35.707 line:80%
Did you presume I could not perceive

00:34:36.624 --> 00:34:38.835 line:80%
what you so plainly see between them?

00:34:41.838 --> 00:34:43.798 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>The Grand Prince smiles</i>
<i>when he drives too.</i>

00:34:43.882 --> 00:34:46.009 line:80%
He can be so childlike sometimes.

00:34:46.092 --> 00:34:48.011 line:80%
He's in danger right now!

00:34:48.845 --> 00:34:50.096 line:80%
I like Seong Huiju.

00:34:52.348 --> 00:34:54.267 line:80%
You have tonight to consider your options.

00:34:55.643 --> 00:34:57.186 line:80%
That is all I can provide you.

00:35:26.466 --> 00:35:28.259 line:80%
[♪ somber music playing]

00:36:43.626 --> 00:36:45.712 line:80%
Do you possess the authority to request…

00:36:48.673 --> 00:36:49.966 line:80%
that I end the regency?

00:36:52.218 --> 00:36:54.012 line:80%
I have a duty to protect the Crown.

00:36:54.804 --> 00:36:55.805 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:36:57.974 --> 00:36:59.142 line:80%
You make it sound…

00:37:01.602 --> 00:37:03.730 line:80%
as though I sought to harm it.

00:37:04.731 --> 00:37:06.482 line:80%
The Crown represents the nation.

00:37:08.067 --> 00:37:10.361 line:80%
As long as you represent the Crown,

00:37:10.445 --> 00:37:11.738 line:80%
you and the Crown

00:37:12.488 --> 00:37:13.781 line:80%
are one.

00:37:15.199 --> 00:37:16.534 line:80%
So?

00:37:18.286 --> 00:37:19.412 line:80%
Face your downfall alone.

00:37:22.248 --> 00:37:23.499 line:80%
I will not allow you

00:37:25.460 --> 00:37:27.170 line:80%
to drag the Crown down with you.

00:37:39.515 --> 00:37:40.516 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:37:49.192 --> 00:37:50.985 line:80%
A private meeting with Prime Minister Min?

00:37:51.069 --> 00:37:53.905 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.
They started early this morning.

00:37:53.988 --> 00:37:55.948 line:80%
It has already been three hours.

00:37:56.491 --> 00:37:58.409 line:80%
The Cabinet must be feeling
the pressure as well.

00:38:02.413 --> 00:38:03.414 line:80%
What about Seong Huiju?

00:38:04.332 --> 00:38:05.458 line:80%
Pardon?

00:38:05.541 --> 00:38:08.419 line:80%
Is the Grand Princess alone right now?

00:38:09.170 --> 00:38:10.213 line:80%
[Huiju] What?

00:38:11.506 --> 00:38:14.092 line:80%
He told him to end his regency?
Jeongwoo did?

00:38:14.175 --> 00:38:15.176 line:80%
[Hyeon] Yes.

00:38:15.259 --> 00:38:18.304 line:80%
I mean, I really trusted
Prime Minister Min.

00:38:18.387 --> 00:38:19.722 line:80%
I know we're in a tight spot and all,

00:38:19.806 --> 00:38:22.266 line:80%
but it's not like he doesn't know
what's going on.

00:38:22.350 --> 00:38:23.935 line:80%
They crossed a line here, didn't they?

00:38:26.562 --> 00:38:28.481 line:80%
The Queen Mother is asking for you.

00:38:28.564 --> 00:38:29.982 line:80%
Well, I'm about to lose it. [scoffs]

00:38:49.418 --> 00:38:50.878 line:80%
How does it feel?

00:38:54.006 --> 00:38:56.467 line:80%
How does it feel to have dragged down

00:38:57.927 --> 00:39:00.388 line:80%
the cherished prince of the nation?

00:39:05.560 --> 00:39:07.353 line:80%
He had his moments of eccentricity

00:39:07.436 --> 00:39:09.605 line:80%
and would sometimes go astray,

00:39:11.357 --> 00:39:13.985 line:80%
but until he met you, I-AN was…

00:39:16.320 --> 00:39:18.072 line:80%
the pride of the Crown.

00:39:23.035 --> 00:39:25.288 line:80%
What did you offer him?

00:39:28.124 --> 00:39:29.959 line:80%
What did he gain

00:39:31.169 --> 00:39:33.129 line:80%
by elevating you so?

00:39:39.927 --> 00:39:40.928 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:39:42.138 --> 00:39:43.598 line:80%
Did you not read the contract?

00:39:45.766 --> 00:39:48.603 line:80%
His Royal Highness
does not want anything from me.

00:39:50.855 --> 00:39:53.566 line:80%
He even settled for three years,
as long as I was with him.

00:39:56.194 --> 00:39:57.737 line:80%
So I simply agreed to do so.

00:40:02.825 --> 00:40:04.410 line:80%
[♪ pensive music playing]

00:40:26.641 --> 00:40:29.268 line:80%
[Yun] <i>How does it feel</i>
<i>to have dragged down</i>

00:40:29.352 --> 00:40:31.812 line:80%
<i>the cherished prince of the nation?</i>

00:40:39.779 --> 00:40:40.780 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:40:41.989 --> 00:40:43.658 line:80%
You should head to the King's Quarters.

00:40:43.741 --> 00:40:45.326 line:80%
Has His Majesty summoned me?

00:40:45.409 --> 00:40:47.328 line:80%
I believe Lord INPYEONG is there

00:40:47.411 --> 00:40:49.121 line:80%
with a formal appeal to the king

00:40:49.205 --> 00:40:50.331 line:80%
and even a public petition.

00:40:56.379 --> 00:40:57.630 line:80%
[Hyejeong] <i>Emergency.</i>

00:40:57.713 --> 00:40:59.173 line:80%
<i>Come to the King's Quarters</i>
<i>when you see this.</i>

00:41:04.679 --> 00:41:06.764 line:80%
THE NOBLE COUNCIL LEADER
AND 190 MEMBERS…

00:41:06.847 --> 00:41:08.140 line:80%
THE LOVE STORY
THAT FOOLED THE NATION…

00:41:08.224 --> 00:41:09.225 line:80%
[Lord INPYEONG] Your Majesty.

00:41:09.892 --> 00:41:11.894 line:80%
The Crown will crumble at this rate.

00:41:11.978 --> 00:41:14.021 line:80%
Even the Grand Prince

00:41:14.105 --> 00:41:16.482 line:80%
cannot defy your royal command.

00:41:17.525 --> 00:41:19.068 line:80%
But Uncle…

00:41:19.151 --> 00:41:20.444 line:80%
Your Majesty!

00:41:22.280 --> 00:41:24.740 line:80%
Have you not heard the rumors
spreading among the people?

00:41:25.533 --> 00:41:28.411 line:80%
-The fire that took the late king…
-That is not true!

00:41:29.161 --> 00:41:30.746 line:80%
Father was not…

00:41:30.830 --> 00:41:32.581 line:80%
The Grand Prince knows that you are weak,
that is why--

00:41:32.665 --> 00:41:34.083 line:80%
[Jung] Your Majesty.

00:41:34.166 --> 00:41:35.751 line:80%
The Grand Prince…

00:41:37.962 --> 00:41:38.963 line:80%
[sighs]

00:41:46.470 --> 00:41:49.390 line:80%
How dare you show
such insolence before His Majesty!

00:41:49.473 --> 00:41:50.850 line:80%
How dare you!

00:41:54.478 --> 00:41:56.272 line:80%
How dare you threaten His Majesty?

00:41:59.608 --> 00:42:00.901 line:80%
Why you…

00:42:01.777 --> 00:42:03.446 line:80%
Uncle…

00:42:04.363 --> 00:42:05.614 line:80%
Enter, Court Lady Jung.

00:42:07.825 --> 00:42:09.702 line:80%
[gasps] Your Royal Highness!

00:42:10.578 --> 00:42:11.662 line:80%
Escort His Majesty out.

00:42:13.581 --> 00:42:15.249 line:80%
Do you not hear me?

00:42:15.333 --> 00:42:16.459 line:80%
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:42:18.836 --> 00:42:20.046 line:80%
Grand Prince…

00:42:23.507 --> 00:42:24.800 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:42:40.107 --> 00:42:42.276 line:80%
Do you think I'm oblivious
to your scheming?

00:42:43.402 --> 00:42:44.403 line:80%
[deeply exhales]

00:42:45.279 --> 00:42:47.573 line:80%
[choking] Your… Royal…

00:42:49.116 --> 00:42:50.117 line:80%
Your Royal Highness!

00:42:52.536 --> 00:42:53.537 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:42:54.121 --> 00:42:55.956 line:80%
Please let him go first…

00:42:56.457 --> 00:42:58.626 line:80%
Are you afraid I will become king?

00:43:04.090 --> 00:43:06.133 line:80%
If you wish to drive me from the palace,

00:43:07.843 --> 00:43:09.053 line:80%
you will

00:43:09.720 --> 00:43:11.222 line:80%
have to kill me first.

00:43:12.890 --> 00:43:14.225 line:80%
Your Royal Highness!

00:43:16.394 --> 00:43:18.020 line:80%
[choking, coughing]

00:43:20.898 --> 00:43:22.858 line:80%
If you threaten my nephew again…

00:43:25.569 --> 00:43:27.321 line:80%
you shall not be granted a merciful death.

00:43:40.501 --> 00:43:42.503 line:80%
[choking, panting continues]

00:43:53.597 --> 00:43:54.974 line:80%
Uncle…

00:44:03.691 --> 00:44:05.651 line:80%
THAT DAY, 3 YEARS AGO

00:44:08.654 --> 00:44:10.573 line:80%
The Queen is inside.

00:44:10.656 --> 00:44:12.700 line:80%
Please wait here for a moment.

00:44:13.826 --> 00:44:14.827 line:80%
Understood.

00:44:17.872 --> 00:44:20.082 line:80%
-[King] Uncle!
-[chuckles]

00:44:24.044 --> 00:44:25.045 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:44:29.925 --> 00:44:31.927 line:80%
[muttering]

00:44:40.269 --> 00:44:42.605 line:80%
[Yun] You intend for Grand Prince I-AN
to ascend the throne?

00:44:44.523 --> 00:44:47.276 line:80%
Have you truly gone mad?

00:44:53.324 --> 00:44:55.284 line:80%
[royal] It will be better than dying.

00:44:57.203 --> 00:44:58.996 line:80%
[Yun] It would be better to die.

00:45:09.840 --> 00:45:11.300 line:80%
I would rather see you dead.

00:45:13.469 --> 00:45:15.179 line:80%
For the sake of the Crown Prince.

00:45:17.223 --> 00:45:18.516 line:80%
[royal] My Queen!

00:45:30.528 --> 00:45:31.529 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:45:31.612 --> 00:45:32.613 line:80%
Yes…

00:45:37.952 --> 00:45:39.787 line:80%
[crying]

00:45:52.341 --> 00:45:53.342 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:45:54.134 --> 00:45:55.135 line:80%
[King] Yes?

00:45:59.431 --> 00:46:00.474 line:80%
If you are ever scared…

00:46:01.058 --> 00:46:03.060 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:46:06.689 --> 00:46:07.898 line:80%
…you must come to me.

00:46:11.569 --> 00:46:12.611 line:80%
Whenever that may be.

00:46:34.008 --> 00:46:35.217 line:80%
Come to me…

00:46:38.470 --> 00:46:39.471 line:80%
whenever you get scared.

00:46:43.392 --> 00:46:45.811 line:80%
Yes, Uncle.

00:47:18.761 --> 00:47:19.762 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:47:20.346 --> 00:47:21.388 line:80%
What?

00:47:22.431 --> 00:47:24.058 line:80%
Did you wrong me somehow?

00:47:28.312 --> 00:47:29.355 line:80%
Earlier…

00:47:33.275 --> 00:47:34.276 line:80%
Sorry.

00:47:36.278 --> 00:47:37.279 line:80%
For what?

00:47:38.405 --> 00:47:39.698 line:80%
That unpleasant sight.

00:47:40.699 --> 00:47:41.700 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:47:42.326 --> 00:47:43.369 line:80%
I thought it was pleasant.

00:47:44.828 --> 00:47:46.163 line:80%
What?

00:47:46.246 --> 00:47:47.247 line:80%
You did well.

00:47:49.166 --> 00:47:50.668 line:80%
You must fight back

00:47:52.002 --> 00:47:53.003 line:80%
if you wish…

00:47:55.255 --> 00:47:56.924 line:80%
to protect something.

00:48:07.601 --> 00:48:09.603 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:48:18.654 --> 00:48:19.947 line:80%
[sighs]

00:48:20.030 --> 00:48:21.532 line:80%
Any likes or dislikes?

00:48:22.783 --> 00:48:23.784 line:80%
All of a sudden?

00:48:25.285 --> 00:48:28.288 line:80%
Well, I like…

00:48:29.623 --> 00:48:33.210 line:80%
Flowers. I do like them the most.

00:48:36.338 --> 00:48:37.548 line:80%
What?

00:48:38.674 --> 00:48:40.759 line:80%
-Not you.
-Pardon?

00:48:41.343 --> 00:48:42.970 line:80%
What does the Grand Prince like?

00:48:43.846 --> 00:48:45.097 line:80%
Oh. I see.

00:48:45.180 --> 00:48:46.640 line:80%
The Grand Prince.

00:48:46.724 --> 00:48:48.434 line:80%
-[chuckling] So silly.
-Unbelievable.

00:48:48.517 --> 00:48:50.728 line:80%
Why do you ask?

00:48:51.270 --> 00:48:54.273 line:80%
More stress is
the only thing waiting for him.

00:48:54.356 --> 00:48:56.567 line:80%
I thought I could do
something nice for him.

00:48:56.650 --> 00:48:58.527 line:80%
Maybe a favorite snack or music?

00:49:00.362 --> 00:49:01.655 line:80%
Let me think.

00:49:02.281 --> 00:49:04.533 line:80%
Black tea? He likes black tea.

00:49:05.492 --> 00:49:07.786 line:80%
He also likes bitter chocolate.

00:49:09.830 --> 00:49:10.831 line:80%
What about music?

00:49:10.914 --> 00:49:13.167 line:80%
Nope. He doesn't like anything loud.

00:49:13.250 --> 00:49:14.418 line:80%
Mmm.

00:49:15.377 --> 00:49:17.671 line:80%
What about his favorite scent?

00:49:17.755 --> 00:49:19.006 line:80%
Scent?

00:49:19.089 --> 00:49:20.674 line:80%
Like incense sticks or diffusers.

00:49:20.758 --> 00:49:23.802 line:80%
That will get you kicked out instantly.

00:49:23.886 --> 00:49:28.098 line:80%
He flipped out the last time
I put on some cologne.

00:49:29.892 --> 00:49:31.518 line:80%
Noted. I should stop.

00:49:35.105 --> 00:49:37.274 line:80%
Did you show
the Grand Princess the same care?

00:49:38.275 --> 00:49:39.276 line:80%
Yes.

00:49:39.777 --> 00:49:41.945 line:80%
One works best without distractions.

00:49:48.076 --> 00:49:49.369 line:80%
What about you, Hyejeong?

00:49:52.122 --> 00:49:53.123 line:80%
Pardon?

00:49:54.625 --> 00:49:58.378 line:80%
I mean, it looks like you just know
the names of flowers.

00:49:58.462 --> 00:50:00.547 line:80%
You don't seem that crazy about tea.

00:50:02.841 --> 00:50:05.594 line:80%
What do you like, Hyejeong?

00:50:07.930 --> 00:50:09.556 line:80%
[♪ romantic pop music playing]

00:50:09.640 --> 00:50:10.766 line:80%
Well…

00:50:17.314 --> 00:50:18.315 line:80%
I…

00:50:23.195 --> 00:50:24.238 line:80%
I was

00:50:25.364 --> 00:50:26.698 line:80%
just curious. That's all.

00:50:29.409 --> 00:50:30.494 line:80%
Such nice weather.

00:50:42.714 --> 00:50:44.716 line:80%
[music continues]

00:50:48.637 --> 00:50:49.638 line:80%
[I-AN grunts]

00:51:18.417 --> 00:51:19.459 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>I'm scared</i>

00:51:21.044 --> 00:51:22.337 line:80%
that my honor will end up…

00:51:26.258 --> 00:51:27.259 line:80%
harming you.

00:51:31.597 --> 00:51:32.598 line:80%
Me too.

00:51:36.351 --> 00:51:38.228 line:80%
I'm scared I might end up…

00:51:41.231 --> 00:51:42.441 line:80%
ruining you.

00:52:14.890 --> 00:52:18.268 line:80%
Seong Huiju!
I know public opinion's in the gutter,

00:52:18.352 --> 00:52:20.270 line:80%
but a prosecutor's investigation?
Seriously?

00:52:20.812 --> 00:52:22.439 line:80%
I'm dying over here with tanking stocks.

00:52:22.522 --> 00:52:25.567 line:80%
What the hell are you talking about?

00:52:32.783 --> 00:52:35.452 line:80%
All the board members
have been subpoenaed.

00:52:38.163 --> 00:52:40.290 line:80%
Father is about to be summoned
at this rate.

00:52:42.876 --> 00:52:45.170 line:80%
Okay, I'll be there this afternoon.

00:52:47.464 --> 00:52:48.632 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:52:48.715 --> 00:52:50.217 line:80%
Is something happening at the company?

00:52:50.300 --> 00:52:53.220 line:80%
No. I guess Father is a bit unwell.

00:52:53.303 --> 00:52:54.346 line:80%
The chairman?

00:52:54.930 --> 00:52:56.723 line:80%
-Then we should visit him--
-No need for all that.

00:52:57.307 --> 00:53:00.310 line:80%
That will only end up attracting a crowd.

00:53:00.394 --> 00:53:02.020 line:80%
It'll be better if I make
a quick run with Aide Choi.

00:53:02.104 --> 00:53:04.314 line:80%
-It's nothing serious anyway.
-But still…

00:53:04.398 --> 00:53:06.191 line:80%
You two need to attend court.

00:53:06.775 --> 00:53:07.859 line:80%
Go on.

00:53:07.943 --> 00:53:10.779 line:80%
Let's have another productive day today.

00:53:11.613 --> 00:53:12.614 line:80%
I'll call you.

00:53:13.198 --> 00:53:14.324 line:80%
Good luck!

00:53:22.541 --> 00:53:23.709 line:80%
Get a car ready.

00:53:24.376 --> 00:53:26.086 line:80%
You want to go now?

00:53:26.169 --> 00:53:27.587 line:80%
Not an escort vehicle.

00:53:28.714 --> 00:53:30.132 line:80%
One that I can drive.

00:53:30.799 --> 00:53:31.800 line:80%
Understood.

00:53:42.644 --> 00:53:44.646 line:80%
[♪ energetic music playing]

00:54:11.590 --> 00:54:12.841 line:80%
What do I have to do?

00:54:15.469 --> 00:54:17.012 line:80%
You must know.

00:54:18.055 --> 00:54:20.766 line:80%
Both the company and the palace
are a complete train wreck.

00:54:20.849 --> 00:54:22.768 line:80%
And there's nothing I can do.

00:54:22.851 --> 00:54:24.186 line:80%
At this rate…

00:54:26.188 --> 00:54:27.481 line:80%
[sighs]

00:54:30.400 --> 00:54:31.651 line:80%
So tell me.

00:54:33.904 --> 00:54:35.238 line:80%
Tell me what I should do.

00:54:40.410 --> 00:54:41.620 line:80%
[sighs]

00:54:43.371 --> 00:54:44.372 line:80%
For now,

00:54:45.832 --> 00:54:46.917 line:80%
do nothing.

00:54:47.501 --> 00:54:50.587 line:80%
-What?
-I'll make sure you don't get hurt, so--

00:54:50.670 --> 00:54:52.130 line:80%
I'm not asking you to protect me.

00:54:58.220 --> 00:55:00.180 line:80%
You're not even pretending now?

00:55:03.183 --> 00:55:04.184 line:80%
What?

00:55:04.267 --> 00:55:05.602 line:80%
You said it was all for show.

00:55:06.603 --> 00:55:07.604 line:80%
You and the Grand Prince.

00:55:17.447 --> 00:55:18.698 line:80%
I don't think that's true now.

00:55:19.991 --> 00:55:22.160 line:80%
[♪ tender music playing]

00:55:22.244 --> 00:55:23.537 line:80%
What's that supposed to mean?

00:55:29.835 --> 00:55:30.919 line:80%
I like him.

00:55:32.254 --> 00:55:33.255 line:80%
The Grand Prince.

00:55:37.884 --> 00:55:38.927 line:80%
A lot.

00:55:51.940 --> 00:55:52.941 line:80%
That is…

00:55:57.279 --> 00:55:58.280 line:80%
quite unfortunate.

00:56:22.179 --> 00:56:23.847 line:80%
To the chairman now?

00:56:31.646 --> 00:56:32.647 line:80%
Let's go now.

00:56:33.648 --> 00:56:34.774 line:80%
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:56:37.527 --> 00:56:38.862 line:80%
I messed up.

00:56:44.409 --> 00:56:46.203 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:56:46.286 --> 00:56:47.329 line:80%
Huiju.

00:56:48.622 --> 00:56:50.290 line:80%
I deceived you…

00:56:53.043 --> 00:56:54.669 line:80%
and hurt the company.

00:56:57.881 --> 00:56:59.299 line:80%
I'm sorry for all of it.

00:57:04.721 --> 00:57:05.722 line:80%
Please help me.

00:57:20.695 --> 00:57:22.489 line:80%
Just this once, please help me, Father.

00:57:25.659 --> 00:57:26.952 line:80%
I want to make things right…

00:57:29.579 --> 00:57:31.039 line:80%
but I don't know how.

00:57:38.088 --> 00:57:40.048 line:80%
And you call yourself a businesswoman…

00:57:45.136 --> 00:57:46.346 line:80%
[sniffles]

00:57:49.015 --> 00:57:50.016 line:80%
Tell me.

00:57:51.059 --> 00:57:52.894 line:80%
Who are you trying to save here? Yourself?

00:57:53.395 --> 00:57:54.604 line:80%
Or the Grand Prince?

00:58:17.544 --> 00:58:20.171 line:80%
Um, I heard you enjoyed black tea.

00:58:23.591 --> 00:58:24.592 line:80%
Thank you.

00:58:31.266 --> 00:58:33.977 line:80%
Perhaps you might consider
taking a few days off?

00:58:36.313 --> 00:58:38.732 line:80%
[sighs] What's going on?

00:58:40.191 --> 00:58:44.821 line:80%
The Prime Minister's Office has requested
that you cease your official duties.

00:58:47.157 --> 00:58:48.158 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:58:48.783 --> 00:58:49.784 line:80%
A request?

00:58:53.872 --> 00:58:55.582 line:80%
-Maybe just for a few days…
-[phone buzzes]

00:58:56.583 --> 00:58:58.209 line:80%
NEW MESSAGE

00:58:58.793 --> 00:59:00.045 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>I'll be there soon.</i>

00:59:03.798 --> 00:59:06.509 line:80%
Do not say anything to my wife.

00:59:07.218 --> 00:59:09.262 line:80%
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

01:00:05.527 --> 01:00:06.528 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

01:00:13.118 --> 01:00:14.494 line:80%
How's your father doing?

01:00:22.627 --> 01:00:24.337 line:80%
What's this? A gift?

01:00:29.884 --> 01:00:30.885 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

01:00:33.012 --> 01:00:34.013 line:80%
Yes?

01:00:45.567 --> 01:00:46.776 line:80%
Let's get a divorce.

01:00:59.122 --> 01:01:01.124 line:80%
[♪ romantic pop music playing]

01:01:22.979 --> 01:01:24.272 line:20%
EPILOGUE

01:01:24.355 --> 01:01:25.356 line:20%
Tell me.

01:01:25.899 --> 01:01:27.650 line:20%
Who are you trying to save here? Yourself?

01:01:27.734 --> 01:01:29.152 line:20%
Or the Grand Prince?

01:01:36.534 --> 01:01:37.619 line:20%
Him.

01:01:42.332 --> 01:01:44.375 line:20%
I can save myself.

01:01:47.921 --> 01:01:48.922 line:20%
You…

01:01:52.467 --> 01:01:54.052 line:20%
Please, Father.

01:02:03.895 --> 01:02:06.814 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

01:02:43.434 --> 01:02:44.936 line:80%
I want to cut my losses.

01:02:45.520 --> 01:02:46.813 line:80%
Let's get a divorce.

01:02:48.064 --> 01:02:49.399 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>Is this how it felt?</i>

01:02:50.942 --> 01:02:53.027 line:80%
[Hyejeong] <i>Are they really</i>
<i>going to get divorced?</i>

01:02:53.111 --> 01:02:55.905 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>You must stop either</i>
<i>the Grand Prince or His Majesty.</i>

01:02:55.989 --> 01:02:57.407 line:80%
Do whatever you must.

01:02:57.490 --> 01:02:58.700 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>But you lost it all.</i>

01:02:59.284 --> 01:03:00.994 line:80%
<i>What could you possibly do for me now?</i>

01:03:01.578 --> 01:03:02.579 line:80%
Did you truly believe

01:03:02.662 --> 01:03:05.456 line:20%
I could not protect us?

01:03:05.540 --> 01:03:07.208 line:20%
[Yun] <i>Surely you do not intend to accept.</i>

01:03:07.292 --> 01:03:10.587 line:20%
<i>I need the girl I hid</i>
<i>brought to the palace.</i>

01:03:10.670 --> 01:03:12.213 line:20%
[I-AN] <i>You did not trust me.</i>

01:03:14.299 --> 01:03:16.092 line:20%
[Lady Choi] <i>The palace gates</i>
<i>will be shut soon.</i>

01:03:17.427 --> 01:03:18.469 line:20%
[Huiju] <i>Let's see this through.</i>

01:03:19.554 --> 01:03:20.638 line:20%
I will be by your side.

01:03:22.390 --> 01:03:24.392 line:20%
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:03:35.695 --> 01:03:39.407 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN